1. Install Dependencies
    pip install -r requirements.txt

2. Register a Face
    python register.py
    Enter student name → Webcam opens → Capture 20 images → Window closes
    Images saved in: student_images/<name>/

3. Train Model
    python train.py
    Trains LBPH model → Saves face_model.yml and labels.pkl

4. Mark Attendance
    python mark_attendance.py
    Webcam opens → Detects and identifies faces → Attendance saved to attendance.csv

5. View CSV Log
    Open attendance.csv in Excel or Notepad:

    Name, Date, Time
    Shikher, 2025-06-17, 11:32:00


